line_1: And each unconquer'd heart the strength of all acquires.
Heroic song from thy free touch acquires
line_2: Its clearest tone, the rapture it inspires;

line_1: Slow, with soft lips, the whirling Can acquires
line_2: The tender skeins, and wraps in rising spires;

line_1: The mind new force, and eloquence acquires,
line_2: And with prophetic voice the dying lips inspires.
